habitat_description:
This species occurs in extreme southeastern Pennsylvania, New Jersey, and the Delmarva Peninsula of eastern Maryland, Virginia, and Delaware (Hulse et al. 2001; Lemmon et al. 2007; Tobey 1985; White and White 2002).

Prefer open habitats for breeding and non-breeding in moist or wet forested areas (Dodd 2013).Habitats include forest and grassy floodplains (Dodd 2013)
